<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨١٦٠]</span> عُمرُ بنُ يَعْقُوبَ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٨١٦١]</span> عُمرُ بنُ يَحيَى، الزُّرَقيُّ، الأَنْصارِيُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أنَّ أَبا بَكرٍ، وَعُمرَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رَوَى عَنهُ عَبدُ اللَّهِ بنُ عَونٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُرْسَلٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٨١٦٢]</span> عُمرُ بنُ يُونُسَ بنِ القَاسِمِ، أَبُو حَفْصٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>، اليَمَامِيُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>سَمِعَ عِكْرِمةَ بنَ عَمَّارٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
